                   <strong> Scholarship Description:</strong>
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                            Bighelp National Merit Scholarship  invites applications from meritorious students who passed their class 10 from a government public school.
                            The key objective of the scholarship is to help poor,but meritorious students of class 10 who have studied in a government public school


                           </p>
                            <h2>
                                <hr>
                                    <strong>Who can apply:</strong>
                                    </h2>
 <p>
 

<ul>
<li>Have studied at a Government/Municipal/Zilla Parishad School in India s</li>
<li>Have passed class 10 in the academic year -18 with GPA 9.8 or above or 98% marks or above </li>
<li>Have annual family income less than INR 1,00,000</li>
<li>Not hold agricultural land more than one acre </li>


</ul>
</p>
